articles.title: Warner finds confidence in the nets ahead of WTC Final and Ashes challenge - ICC Cricket
articles.description: Australia star opener David Warner believed that he was practising better than ever before at the nets, and looked to back his game plan prior to the ICC World Test Championship Final 2023.
